---
title: Ssamjang Pork & Mushroom Lettuce Cups with Sweetcorn Fried Rice
description: Tantalising Asian flavours of garlic, ssamjang paste and oyster sauce overflow in these crisp cos lettuce cups! Juicy pork mince is browned with a medley of spices before layering crunchy veggies and mushrooms, bringing you a bite that packs both unbeatable taste and crunch.
